Earth after drifting through space in hypersleep for 57 years. Although her story is initially met with skepticism, she agrees to accompany a team of Colonial Marines back to LV-426.","genre_ids":[28,53,878],"popularity":12.8941,"vote_count":10609,"poster_path":"/r1x5JGpyqZU8PYhbs4UcrO1Xb6x.jpg","release_date":"1986-07-18","vote_average":7.956,"backdrop_path":"/4kix6fAblJIH6eMs0Ku2loyZJXK.jpg","original_title":"Aliens","original_language":"en"},{"id":2067,"adult":false,"title":"Mission to Mars","video":false,"overview":"When the first manned mission to Mars meets with a catastrophic and mysterious disaster after reporting an unidentified structure, a rescue mission is launched to investigate the tragedy and bring back any survivors.","genre_ids":[878,12,9648],"popularity":2.2321,"vote_count":1530,"poster_path":"/cTKWoBpN5Gvi0vpMb9mLtYlwXqT.jpg","release_date":"2000-03-10","vote_average":6.003,"backdrop_path":"/3No5nC3lwppGHxjcEbJGyFtTJvR.jpg","original_title":"Mission to Mars","original_language":"en"},{"id":766507,"adult":false,"title":"Prey","video":false,"overview":"When danger threatens her camp, the fierce and highly skilled Comanche warrior Naru sets out to protect her people. But the prey she stalks turns out to be a highly evolved alien predator with a technically advanced arsenal.","genre_ids":[53,28,878],"popularity":12.9718,"vote_count":7514,"poster_path":"/2FKjLRt7oK1bRRIrxgWmthbBdFh.jpg","release_date":"2022-08-02","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/sNhzcUw5cg4JwICjnHZ5XhTKNrU.jpg","original_title":"Prey","original_language":"en"},{"id":926,"adult":false,"title":"Galaxy Quest","video":false,"overview":"For four years, the courageous crew of the NSEA Protector —  Commander Peter Quincy Taggart, Lieutenant Tawny Madison, and Doctor Lazarus — set off on a thrilling and often dangerous mission in space ... until their series was cancelled! Now, twenty years later, aliens under attack have mistaken the Galaxy Quest television transmissions for \"historical documents\" and beam up the crew of has-been actors to save the universe. With no script, no director, and no clue, the actors must turn in the performances of their lives.","genre_ids":[35,878,12],"popularity":4.0742,"vote_count":2455,"poster_path":"/fZXSwgZknp81vmciTb86rw0MejV.jpg","release_date":"1999-12-25","vote_average":7.082,"backdrop_path":"/yzQ0mkz1OUJKtUK1NWp53jiGcaJ.jpg","original_title":"Galaxy Quest","original_language":"en"},{"id":2097,"adult":false,"title":"Gappa, the Triphibian Monster","video":false,"overview":"An expedition in the South Pacific lands on a tropical island where the natives worship the mysterious deity Gappa. An earthquake opens up an underground cavern and a baby reptile is discovered inside. The natives warn the foreigners to leave the hatching alone, but they don't listen and take it back to a zoo in Japan. Soon after, moma and papa Gappa start smashing Tokyo looking for their kidnapped child.","genre_ids":[27,878,28],"popularity":0.9776,"vote_count":48,"poster_path":"/pS2NY8VZlkKGyCE5hwZpTbu8exu.jpg","release_date":"1967-04-22","vote_average":5.615,"backdrop_path":"/ugVdGHicz21A3JjSctP1SlpF3e4.jpg","original_title":"大巨獣ガッパ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":2101,"adult":false,"title":"The Brother from Space","video":false,"overview":"A spaceship lands in a small town in Arizona, leaving behind mysterious capsules from which a strange creature emerges and turns out to be the only survivor. Jenny, a blind girl who works as a singing teacher and has paranormal powers, senses the presence of the alien, who is lost and in need of help.","genre_ids":[878],"popularity":0.3089,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/4VaQkchsVqkvMHHmTdlc8Bs6GBA.jpg","release_date":"1988-01-01","vote_average":2.5,"backdrop_path":"/cp20sddQf5SLFvXWsSuXEZUEWuJ.jpg","original_title":"Fratello dello spazio","original_language":"en"},{"id":2114,"adult":false,"title":"Final Fantasy: The Spirits Within","video":false,"overview":"Led by a strange dream, scientist Aki Ross struggles to collect the eight spirits in the hope of creating a force powerful enough to protect the planet. With the aid of the Deep Eyes Squadron and her mentor, Dr. Sid, Aki must save the Earth from its darkest hate and unleash the spirits within.","genre_ids":[12,28,14,878,53,10749,16],"popularity":2.3804,"vote_count":1554,"poster_path":"/47b1EwFqqSWxYna7NtUM7iML4oT.jpg","release_date":"2001-07-02","vote_average":6.195,"backdrop_path":"/qyOO0dgss0oeUYFPWbbdALDgOSm.jpg","original_title":"Final Fantasy: The Spirits Within","original_language":"en"},{"id":828,"adult":false,"title":"The Day the Earth Stood Still","video":false,"overview":"An alien and a robot land on Earth after World War II and tell mankind to be peaceful or face destruction.","genre_ids":[878,53,18],"popularity":2.5639,"vote_count":1205,"poster_path":"/eslDNzf0LF1m9GsgUXlmyfTcC6Y.jpg","release_date":"1951-09-18","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/qwZRvb0DJ5IwDoRuKDRCBuHWzkw.jpg","original_title":"The Day the Earth Stood Still","original_language":"en"},{"id":830,"adult":false,"title":"Forbidden Planet","video":false,"overview":"Starship C57D travels to planet Altair 4 in search of the crew of spaceship \"Bellerophon,\" a scientific expedition that has been missing for twenty years. They find themselves unwelcome by the expedition's lone survivor and warned of destruction by an invisible force if they don't turn back immediately.","genre_ids":[878,12],"popularity":2.1446,"vote_count":1028,"poster_path":"/aq0OQfRS7hDDI8vyD0ICbH9eguC.jpg","release_date":"1956-03-02","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/9EUmwXS6EbY5djAhLtBGzUbBwNV.jpg","original_title":"Forbidden Planet","original_language":"en"},{"id":831,"adult":false,"title":"This Island Earth","video":false,"overview":"Aliens have landed and are hiding on Earth, but need Earth’s scientists to help them fight an inter-planetary war.","genre_ids":[878,12,27],"popularity":0.6425,"vote_count":228,"poster_path":"/2viRDpHmhzQoreZok2auLjkVbSE.jpg","rel